	<owl:Ontology rdf:about="https://spec.edmcouncil.org/fibo/ontology/FBC/FunctionalEntities/CommercialRegistrationAuthorities/">
		<rdfs:label>Commercial Registration Authorities Ontology</rdfs:label>
		<dct:abstract>This ontology specifies definitions for a number of organizations that provide broad based data services, including registration services, such as market data providers, instrument identifier issuers, organizations that provide exchanges in multiple countries, and the like. It is not intended to be exhaustive, but covers the primary LOUs for LEI issuance among others. Note that this ontology only provides reference data, no additional semantics.</dct:abstract>
